title: Orange Cake Explosion Death
story: dungeo
description: ADR-227 Phase 2 - eating the orange-icing cake (ORICE "Explode") is terminal death via the CakeEatingInterceptor

---

# Setup - light + teleport to Tea Room
> gdt
[OK: contains "GDT ready"]

> tk brass lantern
[OK: contains "Taken"]

> ex
[OK: contains "Returning"]

> turn on lantern
[OK: contains "switches on"]

> gdt
[OK: contains "GDT ready"]

> ah Tea Room
[OK: contains "Teleported"]

> ex
[OK: contains "Returning"]

# Eating the orange cake explodes -- terminal death
> eat orange cake
[OK: contains "explode"]
[EVENT: true, type="if.event.player.died" cause="cake_explosion"]
